name: noi to the moon
description:
(to the moon, is the beginning of the journey of my characters, you could say as an introduction / born in the metaverse)

this time there is Neo, Neo is a kind of cat from the world of VetteMagu, he belongs to the vette clan, he looks very indifferent and doesn't care about anything but actually he is kind, care and wise. he will start his journey in metaverse world by using a rocket.

rocket components:
9 skulls:Neo has 9 lives
Cabin like the Televison n components like the keyboard identify the metaverse
components like the music player and loudspeakers (beside) aim to make the journey comfortable and sustainable.

hope neo glides smoothly on the moon :)
